	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002384_0001"/><!--pb/@n='01'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>50, ALBERMARLE S<hi rend="sup">T</hi></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">W. </p>
<lb/><p rend="right">7 August </p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1865 </p>
<lb/><p rend="left">Dear <del type="cancelled">Lady Franklin</del></p>
<lb/><p>We did not 
<lb/>forget your kind 
<lb/>invitation at 
<lb/><persName>Lady Palmerston's</persName>
<lb/>but when at the 
<lb/>door on our 
<lb/>way to tea with 
<lb/>you we <choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice>
<lb/>letters announcing 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002384_0002"/><!--pb/@n='02'-->
<lb/>the illness of a friend 
<lb/>and we went off 
<lb/>for medical aid 
<lb/>instead. We have 
<lb/>been at <placeName>Newstead 
<lb/>Abbey</placeName> till this 
<lb/>moment and 
<lb/>hearing at <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Murray's</persName>
<lb/>that you are to 
<lb/>have an evening 
<lb/>for <persName>Queen Emma</persName>
<lb/>and I trust you 
<lb/>will allow me 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002384_0003"/><!--pb/@n='03'-->
<lb/>to bring my daughter 
<lb/>to it. We are at 
<lb/><placeName>48 Euston Square</placeName><reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
		</body>
